Commentary Text: Harshal Patel to Chris Morris, out Caught by Padikkal!! Wow! That's a stunning catch. Harshal is on a hat-trick, again. Can he? Commentary Text: Chahal to Livingstone, out Caught by de Villiers!! This is a body blow for RR. Livingstone had to be the one to take them to a competitive total but he's perished while trying to clear the fence. This is a typical Chahal wicket. He knows the batter is coming after him and hence floats it outside off, Livingstone moves across and drags it the leg-side, not off the middle and a simple catch for AB at long-on. RR have completely lost their way, going from 100/1 to 127/6. Livingstone c de Villiers b Chahal 6(9)

Commentary Text: Chris Morris to Kohli, out Kohli Run Out!! A fantastic effort by Parag that! He has nailed a direct-hit at the bowler's end from point and that brings an end to Kohli's innings. Virat was a bit hesitant to take the run initially, but he goes for it and has to pay the price for it as he is comfortably outside the crease at the other end. Was sliced towards point by him where the fielder stopped it with a dive. Does well to get back and fire a throw at Kohli's end. Was actually a misfield by the fielder and they decided to take a chance. Both the openers are back to the hut. Kohli run out (Riyan Parag) 25(20) [4s-4]
